Hero/Description/Abathur=Does not directly engage in combat, but rather can act through his allied Heroes and minions and place Toxic Nests to defend important locations.
Hero/Description/Arthas=Engages with his enemies directly, freezing and slowing them. Summons undead spirits of enemy Heroes he kills to fight for him.
Hero/Description/Barbarian=A direct fighter who uses Fury instead of mana. Leeches life from enemies by attacking and using abilities.
Hero/Description/DemonHunter=Strikes at the enemy from afar and gains Hatred, increasing her attack speed. Can Vault away if enemies get too close.
Hero/Description/Diablo=An aggressive ability driven hero that charges his enemies and uses flame and lightning to burn them down. Reveals critically damaged Heroes.
Hero/Description/Falstad=Able to strike enemies from afar and fly over any terrain. Uses abilities to avoid damage or destroys his enemies.
Hero/Description/Illidan=Marks his targets by using his abilities. Attacks against marked targets reduce his cooldowns. Moves quickly to pursue his foes.
Hero/Description/Kerrigan=An aggressive hero that gains temporary shielding by attacking enemies and using her abilities. Able to stun enemies and pull them towards her.
Hero/Description/L90ETC=A heavy front-line hero that knocks around and stuns his foes while buffing his allies. Able to leap anywhere on the battleground.
Hero/Description/Malfurion=Heals allies and restores their mana. Able to reveal and root groups of enemies from a distance.
Hero/Description/Muradin=Jumps around the battleground and stuns Heroes. Rapidly regenerates health as he nears death.
Hero/Description/Nazeebo=Effective against groups of enemies, summoning Spiders, Zombies, and Frogs. Siphons health and mana from dying foes.
Hero/Description/Nova=Automatically cloaks while out of combat. Snipes enemies from afar, and creates Decoys of herself to fool enemies.

Hero/Description/Tassadar=Can grant a temporary shield to allies, detect nearby enemy Heroes, and manipulate the battleground for his team.

Hero/Description/Tychus=Fights enemies up close and personal, and then shoots them as they run away.
Hero/Description/Tyrael=Protects his allies by transferring damage from them and can absorb a lot of damage. Explodes when he dies damaging nearby enemies.
